@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eigouh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.82) * (tmp + 0.36 + v0 + 0.55)) - wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = ((v1 - v0) - wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.11)))
    v0 = (v0 * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.33) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.22)))
    v0 = (tmp / wp.exp((v2 + 0.11 + v0 + 0.49)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.37) / 0.16) - (0.01 / (tmp + 0.36 / v1 + 0.31)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin(v1))
    tmp = 0.84
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
